   20: -module(gb_sets_property_test_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   23: 
   24: -compile(export_all).
   25: -compile(nowarn_export_all).
   26: 
   27: all() -> [
   28:           add_case,
   29:           balance_case,
   30:           delete_case, delete_any_case,
   31:           difference_case,
   32:           from_ordset_case,
   33:           insert_case,
   34:           is_member_case,
   35:           iterator_case, iterator_from_case,
   36:           larger_case,
   37:           largest_case,
   38:           singleton_case,
   39:           smaller_case,
   40:           smallest_case,
   41:           take_largest_case,
   42:           take_smallest_case
   43:     ].
   44: 
   45: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   46:     ct_property_test:init_per_suite(Config).
   47: 
   48: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   49:     Config.
   50: 
   51: add_case(Config) ->
   52:     do_proptest(prop_add, Config).
   53: 
   54: balance_case(Config) ->
   55:     do_proptest(prop_balance, Config).
   56: 
   57: delete_case(Config) ->
   58:     do_proptest(prop_delete, Config).
   59: 
   60: delete_any_case(Config) ->
   61:     do_proptest(prop_delete_any, Config).
   62: 
   63: difference_case(Config) ->
   64:     do_proptest(prop_difference, Config).
   65: 
   66: from_ordset_case(Config) ->
   67:     do_proptest(prop_from_ordset, Config).
   68: 
   69: insert_case(Config) ->
   70:     do_proptest(prop_insert, Config).
   71: 
   72: is_member_case(Config) ->
   73:     do_proptest(prop_is_member, Config).
   74: 
   75: iterator_case(Config) ->
   76:     do_proptest(prop_iterator, Config).
   77: 
   78: iterator_from_case(Config) ->
   79:     do_proptest(prop_iterator_from, Config).
   80: 
   81: larger_case(Config) ->
   82:     do_proptest(prop_larger, Config).
   83: 
   84: largest_case(Config) ->
   85:     do_proptest(prop_largest, Config).
   86: 
   87: singleton_case(Config) ->
   88:     do_proptest(prop_singleton, Config).
   89: 
   90: smaller_case(Config) ->
   91:     do_proptest(prop_smaller, Config).
   92: 
   93: smallest_case(Config) ->
   94:     do_proptest(prop_smallest, Config).
   95: 
   96: take_largest_case(Config) ->
   97:     do_proptest(prop_take_largest, Config).
   98: 
   99: take_smallest_case(Config) ->
  100:     do_proptest(prop_take_smallest, Config).
  101: 
  102: do_proptest(Prop, Config) ->
  103:     ct_property_test:quickcheck(
  104:         gb_sets_prop:Prop(),
  105:         Config).
